<item>
            <title>[SOLR-3824] Velocity: Error messages from search not displayed</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-3824</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Error messages are not displayed in Solritas GUI.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Example: In SolrCloud mode I have two shards, but shut down shard B. Then there is an error message:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;lst name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;error&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;str name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;msg&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;no servers hosting shard:&amp;lt;/str&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;code&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;503&amp;lt;/&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;/lst&amp;gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;However this is not displayed by Velocity template, it shows an empty search result.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
